  "remarks": "Eduard Bazhenov is a General Director of the Russian military industry company JSC SDB Turbina. The company produces power solutions that are used by other Russian military industry companies for the fulfilment of state defence orders. JSC SDB Turbina produces gas turbines for MSTA-S howitzers that are used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation during Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
